{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"532","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"具毒性！二甲基乙醯胺引起疾病將納職業病項目","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:'>2019-09-06 16:59</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:'>&nbsp;<img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E5%8B%9E%E4%BF%9D%E8%81%B7%E6%A5%AD%E7%97%85.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 672px;' /></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'>勞動部將預告「增列勞工保險職業病種類項目」修正草案。（記者李雅雯攝）</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>〔記者李雅雯／台北報導〕勞動部將在下週預告「增列勞工保險職業病種類項目」修正草案，規劃將新增「二甲基乙醯胺引起之疾病及其續發症」為職業病項目。「二甲基乙醯胺」是具有肝毒性、神經毒性、生殖毒性、皮膚與眼睛刺激性的有機溶劑，廣泛地用於化學纖維、石油加工和藥品製造等領域。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>勞動部勞動保險司職災保險科長林煥柏說明，該次提案由台灣環境職業醫學會提出，經過職業醫學專科醫師和相關醫學會討論，認為該物質的危害暴露和疾病間的因果關係明確，因此新增「二甲基乙醯胺引起之疾病及其續發症」為職業病項目。過往國內發生過<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>個因為二甲基乙醯胺而急性中毒的案例，國外案例則已累積數件，。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>勞動部規劃將在下週預告「增列勞工保險職業病種類項目」修正草案，各界可在<span lang='EN-US'>11</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>日前提出建議。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'>資料來源：<span lang='EN-US'>https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2908066</span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2019-09-11","clk_count":"212"}},"__N_SSG":true}